value: Swish needs accessibility permissions to function properly.
Click the lock on the bottom left to authenticate, then check Swish in the application list.
You can always access this window by opening Swish via Finder or Launchpad.
Swish will provide haptic feedback if enabled via System Settings.
Depending on your hardware, you might want to decrease sensitivity.
Cancel gestures by pressing Esc or resting for the specified timeout.
